27:59.352 --> 28:02.876
And that's our Savior Jesus, Yeshua, Hamashiah.

28:03.597 --> 28:08.562
So no matter how chaotic and dangerous the world appears to be, the question is,

28:08.770 --> 28:12.734
Are you ready for the soon and sudden appearing of the Lord to be ready?

28:12.774 --> 28:14.516
The gospel is very clear.

28:15.017 --> 28:18.440
Jesus didn't say, I am a way to God.

28:18.941 --> 28:21.223
He said emphatically, I am the way.

28:21.884 --> 28:27.810
So I urge you to believe on the Lord Jesus the Messiah and the Bible promises you shall be saved.

28:28.290 --> 28:28.611
Amen.

28:29.672 --> 28:35.538
Meanwhile, we'd love to hear from you on the various social media or through our free Jerusalem channel mobile app.

28:36.162 --> 28:45.374
Please follow all my articles at substack.com and all our videos at our website, exploits.tv and our Jerusalem channel, YouTube platform.

28:45.915 --> 28:58.592
Finally, we invite you to sign up for our weekly email alert called exploits based upon Daniel 1132 declaring the people who know their God will be strong, not weak, and will accomplish biblical exploits.

28:59.013 --> 29:02.738
The works of the Lord in the remaining time before His imminent return.

29:03.618 --> 29:09.657
Let's keep contending for the faith and praying prophetically for the peace of Jerusalem.

29:10.279 --> 29:13.970
I'm Christine Dark, Shalom and Maranatha.

